# Trivy vulnerability suppressions
#
# Add CVE IDs here (one per line) for findings that are confirmed false positives
# or accepted risks after review. Always include a comment explaining why.
#
# Format:
#   CVE-YYYY-NNNNN   # reason — reviewed by <who> on <date>
#
# Example:
#   CVE-2023-2976    # guava: affects server-side RPC only; not used in this app
